---
title: Prosciutto Chicken & Roasted Artichokes with Creamy Burst Tomato Penne & Spicy Breadcrumbs
description: Elegant and flavorful, prosciutto-wrapped chicken cutlets make any night a special occasion. Here, we roast them along with tender artichoke hearts and serve it all over penne pasta tossed in a creamy sauce with blistered grape tomatoes. A shower of spicy herbed breadcrumbs adds the final layer of crunch to this restaurant-inspired dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663a58e9be3ee05a950c384e-2ab7ee5d.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/663a58e9be3ee05a950c384e-en-US.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Southern Europe
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/prosciutto-chicken-and-roasted-artichokes-663a58e9be3ee05a950c384e
